publicwhip.spmotion: *S3M-690 Tricia Marwick: East Fife Male Voice Choir—That the Parliament congratulates the East Fife Male Voice Choir which celebrates its 50th anniversary in 2007; recognises the contribution it makes in raising funds for local charities, and looks forward to welcoming the choir to the Parliament on Wednesday 31 October 2007 for a concert in the Garden Lobby.
